1. Download and extract the Flex 4 SDK to a directory of your choice. 
2. Define FLEX_HOME environment variable with a full path to Flex4 SDK folder.

On Mac or Linux:

$ export FLEX_HOME=/specify-full-path-to/flex4_sdk
(in ~/.bash_profile e.g.)

on Win:

$ set FLEX_HOME=/specify-full-path-to/flex4_sdk

3. Run apache ant task in eclipse.

4. (OPTIONAL) Install FDT Eclipse plugin (or any other) for better code editing.